## Goal
Detect when the stack is behind origin/main and needs rebasing.

## Implementation

```typescript
// src/git/rebase.ts

async function isStackBehindMain(): Promise<boolean> {
  const defaultBranch = await getDefaultBranch();

  // Fetch latest
  await $\`git fetch origin \${defaultBranch}\`;

  // Get merge-base
  const mergeBase = await $\`git merge-base HEAD origin/\${defaultBranch}\`.text();

  // Get current main tip
  const mainTip = await $\`git rev-parse origin/\${defaultBranch}\`.text();

  // If merge-base != main tip, we're behind
  return mergeBase.trim() !== mainTip.trim();
}

async function getCommitsBehind(): Promise<number> {
  const defaultBranch = await getDefaultBranch();
  const result = await $\`git rev-list HEAD..origin/\${defaultBranch} --count\`.text();
  return parseInt(result.trim(), 10);
}
```

