## Design Rationale

**Why preserve tree instead of re-merge?**
- No new merge conflicts introduced
- Merge resolution preserved exactly
- Better performance (no merge computation)

**Why use commit IDs instead of hashes?**
- Hashes change on rebase
- Commit IDs are stable identifiers

